{"tid":1534861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[代樓主重開][法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 再告埋香港警察同港鐵！！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T01:19:55.000Z","uid":58434,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3d016bca2c35aeb7662c54ca645226eac5334f","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"前幾日發夢同法律界朋友傾偈，講起話太子站可能真係死左人，跟住其中一個 (姑且叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 就講左以下既野:- <br />\n<br />\n要知有冇死人一定要攞CCTV啦，而家要搵個人係政府出黎講大話容乜易<br />\n<br />\n其實要攞法庭命令迫佢地交CCTV好易姐，兩個做法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第一個做法</span></strong>《高等法院條例》第41條講明法庭可以俾pre-action discovery架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n拿我驚你唔明，pre-action discovery姐係&quot;在法律程序展開前命令將文件披露等的權力&quot;，即係話如果<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有人有意欲告香港警察同港鐵既話</span>，係可以係告之前申請要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法庭俾強制命令要黨鐵交出831當晚既CCTV</span></span>，再告黨鐵同警察。 有法庭命令黨鐵唔交就係藐視法庭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另一個做法</span></strong>就係告左黨鐵同警察先，再經《高等法院規則》 第24條 文件透露及查閱去攞CCTV又得。<br />\n<br />\n邊種做法都好，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要快</span></span>因為CCTV唔會keep咁耐。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候朋友B<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就問：喂，而家係想知有冇死人喎，點樣告黨鐵同警察呀<br />\n<br />\npost太長，下面繼續"},{"pid":"1ad1e992e1448232d5d878e9d578f763cb7fbdfd","tid":1534861,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:50:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27b25252dc353de36309a0ee807942bb921b2aef","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:50:56.000Z","msg":"朋友A: 傻豬黎既，當然唔可以亂咁告啦，佢地而家好大官威架嘛。但係你唔好唔記得，831同時係一個警察執行，黨鐵放任既恐佈襲撃，理論上任何受到呢次襲撃影響既人都可以告。而咁岩睇番有冇死人同發生咩事都只係順便既姐係咪 <br />\n<br />\n不過要真係執行呢樣野有幾個難題： <br />\n<br />\n1. 要搵到受襲撃影響既人。其中最好既當然係直接俾警察打既人，其次就係當時係車廂既其他人。你知啦睇到呢d咁恐怖既襲擊之後有咩頭暈身熱都係好合理。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 訟費問題：始終呢類既高院案都比較昂貴，一般市民未必負擔得起訟費。 <br />\n<br />\n所以當務之急要做既係兩件事(1) 搵左個受害者出黎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，然後 (2) 睇下佢有冇錢告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有既就要即刻搵律師樓做野喇，最好搵d有幫義士又有做民事訴訟既律師行啦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿最後俾埋d reference你: <br />\n<br />\n《高等法院條例》第41條: <a href=\"http://www.hklii.org/chi/hk/legis/ord/4/s41.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.org%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F4%2Fs41.html&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=3aa0ed02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.org/chi/hk/legis/ord/4/s41.html</a> <br />\n《高等法院規則》 第24條: <a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/reg/4A/s24.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Freg%2F4A%2Fs24.html&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=1ab06c62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/reg/4A/s24.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n然後我就醒左了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f199afe899e7270de1cfdc9f67a8f47b24671388","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:51:41.000Z","msg":"推佢"},{"pid":"f81dab42dfb30f779ca3ce0ddf1f9df035a69660","tid":1534861,"uid":300767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"bc9b6075f6d3d196d7852d5cd00bcefc1be81372","tid":1534861,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e02f7f6f717e8ebea8363eb45abcb8700f9c240e","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"053d3cd4decb80542f14656c4620d7e15c576761","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"幫佢手"},{"pid":"b756feabe1fc1c5f6e14f4623b25bd499a480f7c","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"樓主出現未"},{"pid":"9ab7429a7f74be17b845376f7aef7f9de3a5d9df","tid":1534861,"uid":99695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"25d01586eb0f98153035dc0031e3ef0e15ab0411","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"幫手"},{"pid":"5deb17aee329d828ff8dc0b4ca69b59a4db047a4","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">切勿落單</span></span>"},{"pid":"e286f5b298f163cf5cf62148d0882904dcac24d0","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"b631066ca2c35d5ce7b24f293e14af41fe9228f6","tid":1534861,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"隔離有個ou學生會會長831太子站無條件釋放，推到比所有人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4278168903586e9ce69a72b9298d0ad259d4046d","tid":1534861,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc7df518818da95f911d7fb717292cc19a4493c","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"CCTV!"},{"pid":"3367e96c43ab17b6c0648bd9fbf6b5d2e5e207dc","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b631066ca2c35d5ce7b24f293e14af41fe9228f6","tid":1534861,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"隔離有個ou學生會會長831太子站無條件釋放，推到比所有人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:57:03.000Z","msg":"組隊入站攞呀"},{"pid":"b5fe326655ab7948e7d4a8c05c1a0d13a678de31","tid":1534861,"uid":300536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"麻煩哂！p牌一日一post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfb15314f977e3f5829add9d4092b83ea1e6a90","tid":1534861,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ba0e735c6bcf402dfbbf8bcd8ab6a1304c8c9f","tid":1534861,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:58:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b0285397db353a20bce2b661b47102355cb1927","tid":1534861,"uid":164372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:58:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aad5192d865c31b0fa292b21e10523f6bad0ebf4","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:59:09.000Z","msg":"咩方法都要有"},{"pid":"b423eef7ef8212e28601ad111de22bc73130fa0a","tid":1534861,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"推到有人"},{"pid":"da5ed0e0dba9b9eba0c173521139b00507d170da","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"拎呀"},{"pid":"e444a3df4762cd1e79877183750961081c41130d","tid":1534861,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1分29秒速龍衝入鐵見人就打 到1分40秒佢啲伙計渴班速龍出嚟 入去做乜</span>由此可見本身落鐵拉人係唔預呢一part發生 去到最後同721冇分別</span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以大家一定要集中火力追擊831黑警恐襲太子站旺角站</span></span>\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvIau2kwxzZA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=d209cfa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外好重要好重要好重要</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aoLoCBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaoLoCBH.png&h=99a60b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynKAtJo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynKAtJo.png&h=73eded90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSOBf5z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSOBf5z.jpg&h=5b212764&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9089b320b537c338ca0a13151d7d4c5360acaa45","tid":1534861,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"4d42e42a3520a853311db6e16775674537e16a6d","tid":1534861,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:01:14.000Z","msg":"還清白"},{"pid":"386b53f19f1cc4966f570c4736ddf51a2a4060df","tid":1534861,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n<br />\n有無站內出返黎既證人?"},{"pid":"b0098a79d4e2887e205c5cc19481752e30986310","tid":1534861,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e00e85f66bc2b37dae6b340f6bba4a287f2908","tid":